Bake
====
 
Version: 0.1
Date: March 24th 2009
Author: PhilHawksworth http://hawksworx.com http://twitter.com/philhawksworth

Description
===========

A utility to merge text files into a single output file based on a template and a simple recipe.  Based on Cook by UnaMesa.


Requirements 
============

- Python


Setup
=====

- Place bake.py on your path.


Usage
=====

- Create a recipe file. 
Recipes should be named in this form: NAME[.EXTENSION].recipe
A template
